Mistakes I Made Today

Used checkbox where radio was needed — user could select multiple experience levels
Forgot to give same name to radio buttons — they were not deselecting each other
Did not add a placeholder option in dropdown — user had no default prompt

How I Fixed Them

Rule: multiple selections allowed → checkbox. Only one allowed → radio
Rule: all radio buttons in one group must have exactly the same name
Rule: always add an empty first option in dropdown as a prompt

